SYNOPSIS
  Query a person's love potential

DESCRIPTION
  This is a very difficult task to undertake, do not do 
  it unless you are ready for the consequences.  What
  you do is really look at a possible prospect, I mean
  really look at them, don't just lustily view them.
  What you need to do is compare your outlook on life
  with theirs, try to look inside of their hearts.  If
  you really and truly love them, well, then you
  should go for it.  Good luck.

